== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[804]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – 【Saichō】 (最澄) and 【Kūkai】 (空海) entered Tang China as {{ill|Kentōshi (envoy to Tang China)|ja|遣唐使|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * [[Enbun]] 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1356]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Bunna|ja|文永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Enbun|ja|延文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * [[Keichō]] 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1611]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ascended to Kyoto, calling upon {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyori|ja|豊臣秀頼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} at {{ill|Nijō Castle|ja|二条城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for a meeting, signifying a reversal in the relationship between the Tokugawa and Toyotomi clans. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Shinbutsu Bunri†Shinbutsu_Bunri|ja|神仏判然令|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was promulgated, prohibiting the syncretism of Shinto and Buddhism and mandating the separation of shrines and temples. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 9|ja|5月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Meiji|ja|明治天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} entered Edo Castle from Kyoto, marking the foundation of Tokyo as the new capital.
== Births == * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1676]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fushimi-no-miya Kuninaga Shinnō|ja|伏見宮邦永親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 14th head of the Fushimi-no-miya (died [[1726]]). == Deaths == * [[Tenna]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1682]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nishiyama Sōin|ja|西山宗因|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a renga master (born [[1605]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|May 17|ja|5月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mōri Takachika|ja|毛利敬親|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the head of the Chōshū Domain (born [[1819]]).
