4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 9|ja|5月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Meiji|ja|明治天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} entered Edo Castle from Kyoto, marking the foundation of Tokyo as the new capital.
== Births == * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1676]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fushimi-no-miya Kuninaga Shinnō|ja|伏見宮邦永親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 14th head of the Fushimi-no-miya (died [[1726]]). == Deaths == * [[Tenna]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1682]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nishiyama Sōin|ja|西山宗因|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a renga master (born [[1605]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|May 17|ja|5月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mōri Takachika|ja|毛利敬親|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the head of the Chōshū Domain (born [[1819]]).
