{{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 28''' is the 28th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[804]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=}}) – 【Saichō】 (最澄) and 【Kūkai】 (空海) entered Tang China as {{ill|Kentōshi (envoy to Tang China)|ja|遣唐使|qq=}}. * [[Enbun]] 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1356]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Bunna|ja|文永|qq=}} to {{ill|Enbun|ja|延文|qq=}}. * [[Keichō]] 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1611]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=}} ascended to Kyoto, calling upon {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyori|ja|豊臣秀頼|qq=}} at {{ill|Nijō Castle|ja|二条城|qq=}} for a meeting, signifying a reversal in the relationship between the Tokugawa and Toyotomi clans. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Shinbutsu Bunri†Shinbutsu_Bunri|ja|神仏判然令|qq=}} was promulgated, prohibiting the syncretism of Shinto and Buddhism and mandating the separation of shrines and temples. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 9|ja|5月9日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=}} entered Edo Castle from Kyoto, marking the foundation of Tokyo as the new capital.
== Births == * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1676]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fushimi-no-miya Kuninaga Shinnō|ja|伏見宮邦永親王|qq=}}, the 14th head of the Fushimi-no-miya (died [[1726]]). == Deaths == * [[Tenna]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1682]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Nishiyama Sōin|ja|西山宗因|qq=}}, a renga master (born [[1605]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1871]] {{ill|May 17|ja|5月17日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mōri Takachika|ja|毛利敬親|qq=}}, the head of the Chōshū Domain (born [[1819]]).
