n calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 9|ja|5月9日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=}} entered Edo Castle from Kyoto, marking the foundation of Tokyo as the new capital.
