== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enryaku|qq=}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[804]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 11|qq=}}) – 【Saichō】 (最澄) and 【Kūkai】 (空海) entered Tang China as {{ill|Kentōshi (envoy to Tang China)|ja|遣唐使|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kentōshi (envoy to Tang China)|qq=}}. * [[Enbun]] 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōhei|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1356]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 29|qq=}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Bunna|ja|文永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunna|qq=}} to {{ill|Enbun|ja|延文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enbun|qq=}}. * [[Keichō]] 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1611]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} ascended to Kyoto, calling upon {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyori|ja|豊臣秀頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyori|qq=}} at {{ill|Nijō Castle|ja|二条城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nijō Castle|qq=}} for a meeting, signifying a reversal in the relationship between the Tokugawa and Toyotomi clans. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 20|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Shinbutsu Bunri†Shinbutsu_Bunri|ja|神仏判然令|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinbutsu Bunri†Shinbutsu_Bunri|qq=}} was promulgated, prohibiting the syncretism of Shinto and Buddhism and mandating the separation of shrines and temples. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 9|ja|5月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 9|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Meiji|qq=}} entered Edo Castle from Kyoto, marking the foundation of Tokyo as the new capital.
== Births == * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enpō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1676]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fushimi-no-miya Kuninaga Shinnō|ja|伏見宮邦永親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fushimi-no-miya Kuninaga Shinnō|qq=}}, the 14th head of the Fushimi-no-miya (died [[1726]]). == Deaths == * [[Tenna]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1682]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Nishiyama Sōin|ja|西山宗因|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishiyama Sōin|qq=}}, a renga master (born [[1605]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1871]] {{ill|May 17|ja|5月17日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 17|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mōri Takachika|ja|毛利敬親|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mōri Takachika|qq=}}, the head of the Chōshū Domain (born [[1819]]).
